{"tid":2026835,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩會：因武漢肺炎收集大量人類健康數據 建議中國輸出珍貴的「數據能源」謀取巨大利益","createTime":"2020-05-21T08:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:13:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1249af4819879b2a8c5aeb1c089820c05aa8494f","tid":2026835,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"李小加兩會建議中國為世界經濟發展輸出「數據能源」<br />\n21.05.2020 15:56<br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員、港交所行政總裁李小加向兩會提交建議，指中國可憑藉強大的數據積累和技術軟實力，為下一輪世界經濟發展輸出「數據能源」，建議在中央有關部委領導下，與業界各方建立協作機制，聚焦討論業界關心的核心問題，可從醫療數據著手，共同制訂相應監管規定，加速數據要素市場培育。<br />\n<br />\n他指，醫療數據與人類健康密切相關，可被認為是重要戰略資源，而生物科技發展急需醫療健康數據支持，新型冠狀病毒疫情的防控工作，使得讓渡一部分隱私和信息保護的權利來維護公共衛生安全成為可能；另外，醫療健康數據亦最容易落地，也最能產生經濟效益。他認為在隱私加密保護的前提下，也許政府可收取部分醫療數據市場化帶來的增值稅，用以補貼醫保支出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289078&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289078%26csid%3D261_341&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsTUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=f76cf968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289078&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4341597318ba5ba7ef395289dfaa963a80fa7d9d","tid":2026835,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n[香港文化] 上連登打正字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026832</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce8724d818dcde1ab27b6358830040ae4d715353","tid":2026835,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"公開數據：承認中共病毒源頭來自中國<br />\n不公開數據：隱瞞疫情<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515fe2a236da3362383ca9dc4dbd5eebd6cc6775","tid":2026835,"uid":173179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n原來支那豬而家有新用途<br />\n白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16700d7a3c4f49d0d94c3838a26c746e87ec3568","tid":2026835,"uid":230594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce8724d818dcde1ab27b6358830040ae4d715353","tid":2026835,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"公開數據：承認中共病毒源頭來自中國<br />\n不公開數據：隱瞞疫情<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"百度：中國人願意犧牲私隱換取便利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5524d987b4507650ec3354392489a85ae46e80ab","tid":2026835,"uid":245388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"其實有大陸公司做緊，已經攞左好多人數據。因為大陸對於個人私隱唔太重視，好多人唔知道自己需要維護呢方面權利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果d 公司等於已經有個夾萬，將來只要有條適合嘅key（技術）打開，果d 公司就發達，因為個data base 已經好大，將來好多應用層面都要果d data"},{"pid":"4273d50083789efa88c0830c636f19f92a8d1132","tid":2026835,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4492b390860e19a21ad231c14dd37c6001763aeb","tid":2026835,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"515fe2a236da3362383ca9dc4dbd5eebd6cc6775","tid":2026835,"uid":173179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n原來支那豬而家有新用途<br />\n白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:59:23.000Z","msg":"話明韭菜重有咩用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當子彈射出去都重得"},{"pid":"946e9d1b1baffab502f983956360402ea42bd6a2","tid":2026835,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09